{{!--
  Linguistic style extraction template.

  Variables:
    - character_name: the character's name
    - dialogues: list of dialogue strings from the character
--}}
Analyze the linguistic style of {{character_name}} based on these dialogues:
{{#each dialogues}}
- {{this}}
{{/each}}

Describe:
- Overall style tendencies (formal/informal, terse/verbose, etc.)
- Preferred pronouns and self-references
- Common modal verbs (must, should, might, etc.)
- Common adjectives and descriptors
- 2-3 exemplary utterances as style references
